sentences: André Roligheten (born 2 January 1985) is a Norwegian jazz musician (saxophone) and composer, known from a series of recordings and bands like Albatrosh and Team Hegdal.
In 2008 he finished his Master's degree in improvised music at the Norwegian Academy of Music in Oslo.
2009: 1st prize – "Best Band" at the European Jazz Competition
